idge]]\n| [[A26 road|A26]] near Tonbridge\n|\n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2015|name1= }}\n| [[Catford]]\n| [[Beckenham]]\n| \n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2016|name1= }}\n| [[Plumstead]]\n| [[Erith]]\n| \n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2017|name1= }}\n| [[Strood]]\n| Strood\n| North Street; signed as a spur of the A228\n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2018|name1= }}\n| [[Bexley]]\n| [[Dartford]]\n|\n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2020|name1= }}\n| Unused\n|\n| Ran from [[Aylesford]] to [[Bearsted]]; renumbered in 1977 to its original designation of [[A20 road (England)|A20]]\n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2021|name1= }}\n| [[Willingdon and Jevington|Willingdon]]\n| [[Eastbourne]]\n| \n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2022|name1= }}\n| [[West Wickham]]\n| [[Epsom]]\n| \n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2023|name1= }}\n| [[Hove]]\n| [[West Blatchington]]\n| \n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2025|name1= }}\n| South [[Lancing, West Sussex|Lancing]]\n| North Lancing\n| \n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2026|name1= }}\n| Thames Road, [[Dartford]]\n| Home Gardens, Dartford\n| Previously used for a road in Ewell (now High Street and Kingston Road).\n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2028|name1= }}\n| Unused\n|\n| Ran from what is now B2211 (then part of the A21) to Seven Oaks (now A224).\n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2029|name1= }}\n| A275 near [[Lewes, East Sussex|Lewes]]\n| A26 near Lewes\n|\n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2030|name1= }} \n| [[Bedhampton]]\n| [[Southsea]]\n|\n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2031|name1= }}\n| Offington Lane, [[Worthing]]\n| Teville Road, Worthing\n|\n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2032|name1= }}\n| West [[Worthing]]\n| East Worthing\n|\n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2033|name1= }}\n| A259 at [[Folkestone]]\n| A260 at Folkestone\n| \n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2034|name1= }}\n| [[M20 motorway]] near [[Channel Tunnel]]\n| [[Folkestone]]\n| \n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2036|name1= }}\n| North of [[Bexhill-on-Sea|Bexhill]]\n| East of Bexhill\n|\n|-\n| {{jct|country=GBR|A|2037|name1= }}\n| [[Henfield]]\n| [[Upper Beeding]]\n| 